{"tid":2478080,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國燒酒2選1，IU VS Jennie","createTime":"2021-04-06T19:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-06T19:31:27.000Z","uid":34643,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"784b9c72493e59c1e8778d58221f3392aba59550","tid":2478080,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T19:25:29.000Z","msg":"愛看韓劇的大家，肯定常常在各個韓劇中看過喝酒的場景，戲中角色經常開心的時候喝燒酒，失戀的時候亦是喝燒酒。<br />\n<br />\n韓國燒酒在全世界流行，相信可以歸功於韓劇與流行文化的成功。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tJ8jIJX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtJ8jIJX.gif&h=884a66d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國燒酒常以女藝人當廣告宣傳，甚至在韓國有一說，韓國燒酒瓶上的藝人就是當時最火紅的藝人。<br />\n<br />\n今天就來比拼一下韓國兩大燒酒，你喜歡的是?<br />\n<br />\n真露 VS 初飲初樂<br />\n<br />\n除了燒酒對決亦是人氣比賽哦~<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">IU VS Jennie</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />IU &ndash; 真露<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.luvkpop.com/uploads/2021/02/2021020913485172-311x311.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.luvkpop.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F2021020913485172-311x311.jpg&h=bb92edce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Jennie &ndash; 初飲初樂<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.luvkpop.com/uploads/2021/02/2021020913490827.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.luvkpop.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F2021020913490827.jpg&h=68a63060&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0285ba801b6d386e203ef99dfd978d48edaf98a6","tid":2478080,"uid":170710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T19:28:30.000Z","msg":"連攝影師都知 Jennie 樣衰 唔敢影大頭<br />\nIU完勝"},{"pid":"908e2cd180e7d3387fe0607c76541ac2d3e67cf8","tid":2478080,"uid":308107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T19:31:27.000Z","msg":"個jen乜乜真係好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji